events.name: エントランスへの移動場所

parameters: Clea: General Atu...! Why are you here...!?

General Atu: Hahaha, I am now being pursued as a wicked
person who has conspired with Caron, the former general.

Former General Atu: I have been ordered to be killed by Lex,
specifically!
Mage Relm: This is no laughing matter...!
Thief Nora: Mr. Atu helped the Emma Thief Brigade.
Thief Nora: Is there any way we can ask Mr. Lex for help...?

Former General Atu: Hey hey, causing trouble for your
comrades is the fate of a defeated general, as it has been
determined since ancient times.

Former General Atu: Hahaha, I tried to escape by taking
armor from the guards, but my body is too big and nothing
fits!

Former General Atu: Nevertheless, I have been fortunate
enough to have the opportunity to fight you all seriously in
the end.

Mage Relm: Why did it have to come to this!? I don't want to
fight someone I know anymore!
Thief Nora: I don't want to fight my benefactor either...

Clea: Understood... I have been greatly indebted to you all
until now.
Mage Relm: Wait a minute!? Sophia-san, please stop!

Priestess Sophia: These terrible wounds all over my body...
they were inflicted when I protected all of us.

Priestess Sophia: I want to fulfill General Atu's wish, at
least in the end, when my healing cannot keep up with the
injuries.

Former General Atu: Sigh... I apologize for burdening the
young ones.
Mage Relm: If you say it like that, I can't refuse, can I?!

Thief Nora: Ugh, I don't want to do something like
killing...
Former General Atu: ...Oh, interesting things you say.

Former General Atu: You don't want to kill me? Do you think
I'm an easy target because I'm injured?

Former General Atu: You guys are worried about your own
lives!

Former General Atu: Let's go, heroes of the empire! Dragon
slayers, try to kill me!

Atu: Well done, heroes... I must express my gratitude to
Aktina for allowing me to meet all of you.

Clea: I feel the same way. Thank you, General Atu, for being
here. It's because of you that we were able to come this
far.

Atu: Clea, your sword is gentle... It's so different from
me, who has only sought strength.

Atu: Treasure it... The way of that sword... It embodies the
very essence of the Adventurer's Guild.

Atu: The once praised general being defeated by new heroes,
hahaha, it seems like a subject that would delight the
bards...

Atu: Go... I don't want to see the faces of you all... as
you die...

Clea: Understood... Thank you so much for everything you've
done until now.
Atu: Hahaha... Someday... let's fight again...
Boy: Uncle, are you okay...? Uncle!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
